CustomField.description: Indicates when the RingLead DMS webhook has finished processing a new Marketo record and it can be synced to SFDC. Values can include 'true', 'link_to_account', 'convert_to_contact', and 'Orphan:[SFDC record ID]'. Also, if an existing SFDC record is not synced to Marketo and it is a duplicate of a new Marketo record, the value will be set to 'SF_Orphan:[Marketo record ID].
CustomField.label: RingLead DMS Status
